import React from "react";

import {
    Container,
    ContainerFilter,
    Title,
    ListFilter,
    Row,
    Button,
    Text,
    Image,
    ContainerClosesFilter
} from './styles'
import { DrawerContentScrollView } from '@react-navigation/drawer'
import filter from '../../../assets/Icons/filterblack.png'

import { Ionicons, AntDesign } from '@expo/vector-icons';

export function CustomDrawer(props: any) {
    return (
        <DrawerContentScrollView {...props}>
            <Container>
                <ContainerClosesFilter>
                    <AntDesign name="close" size={24} color="black" />
                    <Image source={filter} />
                </ContainerClosesFilter>
                <ContainerFilter>
                    <Title>Filtrar por:</Title>
                    <ListFilter>
                        <Row>
                            <Button>
                                <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle-outline" size={24} color="#D3E0E2" />
                            </Button>
                            <Text>Chamados atendidos</Text>
                        </Row>
                        <Row>
                            <Button>
                                <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle-outline" size={24} color="#D3E0E2" />
                            </Button>
                            <Text>Aguardando atendimento</Text>
                        </Row>
                        <Row>
                            <Button>
                                <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle-outline" size={24} color="#D3E0E2" />
                            </Button>
                            <Text>Chamados encerrados</Text>
                        </Row>
                    </ListFilter>
                    <Title>Ordernar pelo:</Title>
                    <ListFilter>
                        <Row>
                            <Button>
                                <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle-outline" size={24} color="#D3E0E2" />
                            </Button>
                            <Text>Mais recente</Text>
                        </Row>
                        <Row>
                            <Button>
                                <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle-outline" size={24} color="#D3E0E2" />
                            </Button>
                            <Text>Mais antigo</Text>
                        </Row>
                    </ListFilter>
                </ContainerFilter>
            </Container>
        </DrawerContentScrollView>
    )
}
